  <name>Mullvad VPN</name>
  <summary>The Mullvad VPN client app for desktop</summary>
  <developer id="net.mullvad">
    <name>Mullvad VPN AB</name>
  </developer>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">mullvad-vpn.desktop</launchable>
  <description>
    <p>
      Mullvad VPN is a privacy-focused VPN service. This package provides the
      official desktop client, including the graphical interface, command-line
      tools, and the system daemon that manages secure WireGuard tunnels.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>WireGuard with automatic key rotation</li>
      <li>Multihop, Shadowsocks, and traffic obfuscation</li>
      <li>Advanced kill switch with tight firewall integration</li>
      <li>Split tunneling on Linux</li>
      <li>Custom DNS and content blockers</li>
      <li>Cryptographically signed releases and publicly audited source code</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Mullvad operates under a strict no-logging policy and does not require
      personal information to create an account.
    </p>
  </description>
